query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('aggregation',
'apple-watch',
'arcgis',
'correlation',
'file-transfer',
'genetic-algorithm',
'ivy',
'new-operator',
'omniauth',
'onedrive',
'partial-views',
'production-environment',
'runtime.exec',
'uicolor');
